        <p>Framing contractors operate in a high-volume, time-sensitive world. You're bidding multiple projects simultaneously, scheduling crew weeks in advance, managing lumber deliveries, and often finishing one job to get to the next. Software needs to be fast to use, not an administrative burden.</p>

        <p>Most framing contractors are subcontractors, which changes the software calculus: you need tools for your business, not a GC-level project management suite. Here's what works.</p>

