        <h2>4. Buildertrend — Best for framing GCs</h2>
        <p><strong>Pricing:</strong> Essential $499/mo · Advanced $799/mo · Complete $1,099/mo</p>

        <p>If you operate as a GC — doing framing plus other scopes and managing homeowner clients — Buildertrend is worth the investment. The scheduling, client communication, and change order tools are best-in-class for residential construction. The $499/mo price point only makes sense once you're running multiple projects and billing $1M+ annually.</p>

